# Python Backend

This package is the backend runtime for source management and MCP services.

## Run

```bash
uv sync --project python
PYTHONPATH=python/src uv run --project python agentctl --help
PYTHONPATH=python/src uv run --project python python -m agent_backend.cli --help
PYTHONPATH=python/src uv run --project python python -m agent_backend.session_mcp_server --help
PYTHONPATH=python/src uv run --project python python -m agent_backend.bridge_mcp_server --help
```

## Copilot-style commands

```bash
PYTHONPATH=python/src uv run --project python agentctl auth login --provider github-copilot --from-gh
PYTHONPATH=python/src uv run --project python agentctl auth status
PYTHONPATH=python/src uv run --project python agentctl copilot suggest "find largest files" --shell zsh
PYTHONPATH=python/src uv run --project python agentctl copilot explain --command "git status"
PYTHONPATH=python/src uv run --project python agentctl copilot chat "summarize this repo"
```

Optional model env vars:

```bash
export AGENT_COPILOT_CHAT_URL="https://api.githubcopilot.com/chat/completions"
export AGENT_COPILOT_MODEL="gpt-4.1"
```

## Workspace root contract

Commands expect workspace roots under:

`~/.agent-runtime/workspaces/<workspace-id>`

Source config path:

`<workspace-root>/sources/<source-slug>/config.json`
